OL,5, An IT system is causing key information
OL,6, about court cases in England and Wales 
OL,7, to change or disappear and is putting  
OL,8, justice at risk, the BBC has been told.
OL,10,FOne legal adviser revealed how he      
OL,11,Fentered a driving ban in the system,   
OL,12,Fcalled Common Platform, only to later  
OL,13,Fdiscover the result had changed.       
OL,15,FStaff say warnings about alleged       
OL,16,Ffaults, describing it as "fundamentally
OL,17,Fflawed", have been ignored.            
OL,19,FThe government said there was no       
OL,20,Fevidence justice is being compromised. 
